 Ansley<small><br />Defensive Backs<br /></small>\n*Shannon Dawson<small><br />Offensive Coordinator/Quarterbacks<br /></small>\n*Jimmy Brumbaugh<small><br />Defensive Line<br /></small>\n*[[D. J. Eliot]]<small><br />Defensive Coordinator/Linebackers<br /></small>\n*Tommy Mainord<small><br />Wide Receivers<br /></small>\n*[[Vince Marrow]]<small><br />Tight Ends<br /></small>\n*John Schlarman<small><br />Offensive Line<br /></small>\n*Chad Scott<small><br />Running Backs<br /></small>\n}}\n\n==Depth chart==\n\n{{CFB Team Depth Chart\n| OScheme         = Single Set Back\n| DScheme         = 4-3\n| SpecialTeams    = \n| KeyReserves     = \n| QB_Starter      = 14 '''Patrick Towles'''\n| QB_Backup       = 7 Drew Barker\n| QB_Third        = 12 Reese Phillips\n| RB1_Starter     = 18 '''Boom Williams'''\n| RB1_Backup      = 3 Jojo Kemp\n| RB1_Third       = 4 Mikel Horton\n| RB2_Starter     = \n| RB2_Backup      = \n| RB2_Third       = \n| FB_Starter      = \n| FB_Backup       = \n| FB_Third        = \n| SB1_Starter     = \n| SB1_Backup      = \n| SB1_Third       = \n| SB2_Starter     = \n| SB2_Backup      = \n| SB2_Third       = \n| WR1_Starter     = 13 '''Jeff Badet'''\n| WR1_Backup      = 6 Blake Bone\n| WR1_Third       = 82 T.V. Williams\n| WR1_SchoolName  = \n| WR2_Starter     = 2 '''Dorian Baker'''\n| WR2_Backup      = 9 Garrett Johnson\n| WR2_Third       = \n| WR2_SchoolName  = \n| WR3_Starter     = 9 '''Garrett Johnson'''\n| WR3_Backup      = 1 Ryan Timmons\n| WR3_Third       = 88 Charles Walker\n| WR3_SchoolName  =  \n| WR4_Starter     = \n| WR4_Backup      = \n| WR4_Third       = \n| WR4_SchoolName  = \n| TE1_Starter     = 15 '''C.J. Conrad'''\n| TE1_Backup      = 86 Daryl Long\n| TE1_Third       = \n| TE2_Starter     = \n| TE2_Backup      = \n| TE2_Third       = \n| LT_Starter      = 70 '''Jordan Swindle'''\n| LT_Backup       = 74 Cole Mosier\n| LT_Third        = \n| LG_Starter      = 68 '''Nick Haynes'''\n| LG_Backup       = 75 Zach West\n| LG_Third        = \n| 